name: Stencil painting, untitled (st1)
description:
Untitled 
Spray paint and collage on wood 

Original painting on wood. Made with spray paint and collage on primed wood from stencils designed and created by the artist. Faced with a protective finish and initialed on the back. Artwork dimensions are 4.25" x 6". Each painting is handmade & unique.

Artwork comes framed in a custom made floater style frame. Made from natural un-stained walnut with a semi-gloss finish. Outer frame dimensions are 5.25" x 7". Frames are 1.5" deep.
